===============================================================================
BUGZILLA OVERVIEW
===============================================================================

Noteworthy bugs fixes/enhancements embraced in this release
-----------------------------------------------------------

 GNOME Bugzilla

 * 333528 - Fix random crash when importing CD
 * 399448 - Ensure track column title doesn't get clipped
 * 405798 - Fixed crash when GStreamer reports an error and no track is playing
 * 404939 - Fixed performance regression in taglib-sharp
 
 Novell Bugzilla

 * 200068 - Do not crash when waking from suspend or resetting time (i.e.
            survive DBus restarts; fix in dbus-sharp - Alp Toker)
 * 199893 - Fixed random crash when cancelling import
 * 215045 - Do not allow splash screen to force itself as a permanent top
            level window when starting up
 * 244595 - Startup (and display warning dialog) when a session bus cannot
            be found (DBus)
 * 242345 - Ensure all metadata elements are hidden when engine goes idle
 * 242348 - Allow horizontal scrolling in the radio source

Show all bugs marked FIXED during this release cycle
----------------------------------------------------

 * http://banshee-project.org/files/closedbugs.php/2007-02-05,2007-02-20

File Bugs... Be Proactive... Contribute to Open Source!
-------------------------------------------------------

 * Please do not hesitate to file bugs against Banshee in GNOME Bugzilla.
 * http://bugzilla.gnome.org, component: banshee
 * Discuss Banshee on the mailing list list or in #banshee on irc.gnome.org.
 * Lots of information on the Banshee Wiki: http://banshee-project.org
 * Need to debug Banshee? http://banshee-project.org/Debugging


